### Devops
Github action pipeline is a workflow and each workflow is a yaml files

#### yaml files
*1. Name* workflow/job title

*2. On* Define triggers (Push, PR, Schedule, Manual)

*3. Jobs* Collection of steps that run in parallel by default

*4. Steps* Individual tasks that run in sequence

*5. Actions* Reusable units of code that can be used in jobs

*6. Runner* Environment where jobs run

*7. uses* to use prebuilt actions

